{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"字元編碼","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/character_encoding","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>字元編碼提供了一套編碼系統，使不同的電腦系統或編譯環境可以存在並處理存在於其他語言當中的特殊字元。</p>\n<p>例如在 HTML 中，我們通常使用以下程式碼來宣告一個 UTF-8 的字元編碼:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>這使我們可以在 HTML 檔案中使用幾乎所有人類使用的語言，並且會正常顯示。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"學習更多","title":"學習更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知識","title":"基本知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/International/articles/definitions-characters/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Character encoding on W3C</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Character_encoding\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Character encoding</a> (維基百科)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"學習更多","id":"學習更多"}],"summary":"字元編碼提供了一套編碼系統，使不同的電腦系統或編譯環境可以存在並處理存在於其他語言當中的特殊字元。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Character encoding","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Codificación de caracteres","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Codage des caractères","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Character encoding (文字エンコーディング)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Character encoding","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Character encoding","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Коди